	* file-chooser/gtkfilesystemmatevfs.c:
	(gtk_file_system_mate_vfs_insert_bookmark):
	* libmateui/mate-pixmap.c: (mate_pixmap_new_from_file_at_size),
	(mate_pixmap_load_file_at_size): Init all GError's to NULL.

2007-12-20  Christian Persch  <chpe@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-stock-icons.c:
	* libmateui/mate-ui-init.c: Mark _mate_stock_icons_init with
	G_GNUC_INTERNAL.

2007-12-20  Christian Persch  <chpe@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail.c: (mate_thumbnail_factory_lookup),
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_has_valid_failed_thumbnail),
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_save_thumbnail),
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_create_failed_thumbnail): Adapt to new API
	for g_checksum_get_digest.

2007-12-15  Christian Persch  <chpe@mate.org>

	* configure.in:
	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail.c: (mate_thumbnail_factory_lookup),
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_has_valid_failed_thumbnail),
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_save_thumbnail),
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_create_failed_thumbnail),
	(mate_thumbnail_md5), (mate_thumbnail_is_valid): Use GChecksum. Bug
	#501866.

2007-11-16  Frederic Crozat  <fcrozat@mandriva.com>

	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c: Don't call mateconf to
	get global toolbar style, rely on xsettings instead. Closes bug
	#497380.

2007-11-13  Lucas Rocha  <lucasr@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-client.c (mate_client_post_args_parse): try to get
	the session client ID from DESKTOP_AUTOSTART_ID environment variable
	in case the --sm-client-id is not used. Closes bug #496571.

2007-10-17  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail.c:
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_generate_thumbnail):
	Fix a crash (Fernando, Christian). Closes bug #487117.

2007-10-12  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@novell.com>

	Fix bug #464383 - In the file
	chooser, errors are not reported correctly when creating a folder
	fails.
	
	* file-chooser/gtkfilesystemmatevfs.c
	(gtk_file_system_mate_vfs_create_folder): Use
	MATE_VFS_XFER_ERROR_MODE_QUERY instead of
	MATE_VFS_XFER_ERROR_MODE_ABORT so that our progress/error
	callback will be called if the mkdir() fails.  Patch by Richard
	Hult <richard@imendio.com>.

2007-10-12  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@novell.com>

	Fix bug #485922 - Errors from
	GtkFileSystemMateVFS are not translated, and are too general.

	* file-chooser/gtkfilesystemmatevfs.c (set_vfs_error): Take in a
	'format' argument instead of using hardcoded, untranslated
	strings.
	(get_folder_complete_operation): Use a specific error message for
	set_vfs_error().
	(get_folder_file_info_callback): Likewise.
	(get_file_info_callback): Likewise.
	(create_folder_progress_cb): Likewise.
	(gtk_file_system_mate_vfs_get_parent): Likewise.

2007-10-04  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	Remove these. They haven't been used in ages.

	* tests/Makefile.am:
	* tests/test-icon-theme.c:
	* tests/test-libglade-mate-noupgrade.c:
	* tests/test-libglade-mate.c:
	* tests/test-libglade-mate.glade:

2007-10-04  Christian Persch  <chpe@mate.org>

	* libmateui/Makefile.am: Define MATE_EXPLICIT_TRANSLATION_DOMAIN so
	we get the right _() define. Based on a patch by Takao Fujiwara, bug
	#483263.

2007-10-03  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-client.h: Another typo fix.

2007-10-03  Kjartan Maraas <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c: (create_pixmap),
	(mate_app_install_statusbar_menu_hints),
	(mate_app_find_menu_pos), (per_app_toolbar_style_changed_notify),
	(toolbar_style_changed_notify), (style_menu_item_activated),
	(global_menu_item_activated), (create_and_popup_toolbar_menu): Fix a
	typo in a comment and remove a bunch of trailing whitespace.

2007-10-02  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@novell.com>

	Fix https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=330187 - CD-ROMs
	do not appear in the file chooser.

	* file-chooser/gtkfilesystemmatevfs.c
	(gtk_file_system_mate_vfs_list_volumes): Use the same code as in
	Caja to populate the drive/volume list in the file chooser.
	This way we have the same results, in the same order as Caja.

2007-10-02  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* doc/reference/tmpl/mate-dateedit.sgml:
	* file-chooser/testfilechooser.c: #include <config.h> 
	* libmateui/mate-client.c: Compiler warning fixes.
	* libmateui/mate-dateedit.c: Same
	* libmateui/mate-file-entry.c: Again
	* libmateui/mate-icon-entry.c: Improve string.
	Closes bug #315205.
	* libmateui/mate-icon-item.c: Compiler warnings
	* libmateui/mate-password-dialog.c: Compiler warnings
	* libmateui/mate-propertybox.c: Compiler warnings
	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail.c: Remove obsolete g_chmod
	ripped from glib now that we depend on a newer glib anyway.
	Also fix some warnings from a recent patch.

2007-10-01  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-scores.c: Document the no scores case.

2007-10-01  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-file-entry.c: (browse_dialog_ok),
	(browse_clicked): Fix a crash when user gives a URL
	without trailing '/'.

2007-10-01  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/mate-dateedit.c: (mate_date_edit_set_time),
	(create_children):
	* libmateui/mate-dateedit.h: Add option to show seconds.
	Patch from Goedson Teixeira Paixao <goedson@debian.org>
	Closes bug #473410.

2007-10-01  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* configure.in: Go to 2.21.0.

