2007-07-14  Michael J. Chudobiak  <mjc@cvs.mate.org>

	* NEWS:
	* configure.in:
	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail-pixbuf-utils.c:
	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail.c:
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_generate_thumbnail): Add orientation tag
	support to the thumbnailer. Bumped gtk+ requirement to 2.11.5 
	for orientation support. Removed the internal fast-scaling jpeg 
	decoder, because gdk-pixbuf now provides this feature. 
	Bug #440978.

2007-06-27  Christian Persch  <chpe@mate.org>

	* libmateui/libmateui-2.0.pc.in: Fix the build. Bug #451425.

2007-06-26  Kjartan Maraas <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/libmateui-2.0.pc.in: Add libmatecomponentui-2.0 to Requires
	again since it seems we broke the build in at least mate-panel.
	Both mate-app.h and mate-app-helper.h exposes MateComponentDock and
	MateComponentDockItem.

