	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail-pixbuf-utils.c:
	(_mate_thumbnail_load_scaled_jpeg): Set 
	"mate-original-width/height" properties in the generated pixbuf.
	* libmateui/mate-vfs-util.c: (size_prepared_cb),
	(mate_gdk_pixbuf_new_from_uri_at_scale): Set 
	"mate-original-width/height" properties in the generated pixbuf.
	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail.c:
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_generate_thumbnail),
	(mate_thumbnail_factory_save_thumbnail):
	Set the "mate-original-width/height" properties as metadata in the 
	generated thumbnail. Preserve such info if the helper thumbnailer 
	already provided it.

	Correctly set tEXt::Image::Width and tEXt::Image::Height metadata 
	tags in thumbnails. Closes bug #143470 and bug #356930.

