=========================== 2.17.90 ============================

2007-01-22  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* NEWS: Update.
	* libmateui/0ChangeLog.2003: Rename ChangeLog to this to
	avoid prepare-ChangeLog.pl putting changelog entries in the wrong
	file.

2007-01-21  Chris Wilson <chris@chris-wilson.co.uk>

	Bug 398357 ‚Äì Does not include $(X_CFLAGS)

	X_CFLAGS are used for testing the presence of libSM during
	configure, but not whilst building. This results in a build
	failure under a hosted environment.

	* configure.in:
		Fix the asymmetry and the X_CFLAGS to LIBMATEUI_CFLAGS.

2007-01-15  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

        * mate-thumbnail.c: (mate_thumbnail_factory_finalize),
	  (mate_thumbnail_factory_instance_init): Fix GMutex leak.
	  Patch from Jens Granseuer. Closes bug #396075.

2007-01-15  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* demos/animator_demo.c: (main):
	* demos/mdi_demo.c: (main):
	* demos/test-file-saver.c: (main):
	* demos/test-recently-used.c: (main):
