	* file-chooser/Makefile.am: add WARN_CFLAGS to INCLUDES.

2006-08-21  Tor Lillqvist  <tml@novell.com>

	* libmateui/mate-ui-init.c: Include <gdk/gdkx.h> only if
	GDK_WINDOWING_X11.

2006-08-18  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* NEWS: Update some.
