	No code is touched by these changes. :-)

	* libmateui/mate-multiscreen.c: API doc fixes
	* libmateui/mate-password-dialog.c: Same
	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail-pixbuf-utils.c: Same
	* libmateui/mate-thumbnail.c: Same.

