	* file-chooser/gtkfilesystemmatevfs.c: Implement bookmark 
	renaming.  (#171264)

2005-05-16  Tor Lillqvist  <tml@novell.com>

	* libmateui/mate-ui-init.c (libmateui_module_info_get): As we
	do include mate-client also on Win32 now (see below), do include
	its module info.

2005-05-13  Tor Lillqvist  <tml@novell.com>

	* libmateui/Makefile.am: Do include mate-client.c also on
	Win32. Presumably doesn't do anything awfully useful without any
	Win32-specific code, but having it in libmateui means that apps
	that call its functions don't need to ifdefify those calls.

	* libmateui/mate-client.c: Remove unnecessary includes.

2005-05-11  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmateui/ChangeLog-19990928: Typos
	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c: Same

2005-03-23  Dennis Cranston <dennis_cranston@yahoo.com>

	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c:
	HIG Fix: use header capitalization for game menu items.
	Closes bug #171435.

2005-05-11  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* configure.in:
	* libmateui/mate-multiscreen.c: Fix build on Apple Darwin.
	Patch from Hans Petter Jansson <hpj at novell com>. Closes
	bug #166087.

