	* file-chooser/gtkfilesystemmatevfs.c (fs_module_init): Ref the
	type class that we register so that the module won't get unloaded.
	I'd rather do this with g_module_make_resident(), but at this
	point in the code we don't have access to the GModule.  Fixes
	#139254.

