	Add a new "filechooser-action" property so we can use file
	entries in other modes e.g. save mode. API addition approved
	by the release team.

	* libmateui/mate-file-entry.c: (mate_file_entry_class_init),
	(fentry_set_property), (fentry_get_property): impl. the
	"filechooser-action" property.
	(browse_clicked): construct the file chooser with the appropriate
	GtkFileChooserAction and also append the appropriate buttons
	for that action.

