	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c, mate-app-helper.h,
	mate-client.c, mate-client.h, mate-color-picker.c,
	mate-dateedit.c, mate-dialog-util.c, mate-dialog.c,
	mate-dialog.h, mate-druid-page-edge.c,
	mate-druid-page-edge.h, mate-druid-page-standard.h,
	mate-druid-page.c, mate-druid.c, mate-entry.c,
	mate-file-entry.c, mate-href.c, mate-icon-entry.c,
	mate-icon-list.c, mate-icon-list.h, mate-icon-sel.c,
	mate-mdi-session.h, mate-messagebox.c, mate-messagebox.h,
	mate-pixmap-entry.c, mate-pixmap-entry.h, mate-popup-menu.c,
	mate-scores.c, mate-scores.h, mate-ui-init.c, mate-window.h:
	Lots of little changes to the API documentation comments (adding
	parameters, removing old no-long-existing parameters, matching
	variable names between function declarations and definitions).
	This makes the API docs, such as they are, now build with 250
	less warnings so that we can detect the real problems.

	* doc/reference/tmpl/mate-about.sgml, mate-app-helper.sgml,
	mate-client.sgml, mate-dialog.sgml,
