2002-02-26  Richard Hult  <rhult@codefactory.se>

	* libmateui/mate-dateedit.c (select_clicked): Don't #if 0 the
	grab, otherwise we can't close the popup without selecting a
	date, and the code to handle Escape won't work either.
	(create_children): Don't set vertical size request to 0! Change to
	-1. 
	Use OUT shadow. IN looks really weird here.
	(position_popup): Get the width/height from the allocation instead
	of trying to get it from the window size (which doesn't work
	because GtkButton is NO_WINDOW now).

