2002-02-21  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@ximian.com>

	* libmateui/mate-dialog.c: Use
	g_signal_* and g_object_* instead of gtk_signal_* and
	gtk_object_*, respectively.
	* libmateui/mate-dateedit.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-color-picker.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-client.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-appbar.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-app-util.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-dialog-util.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-druid.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-druid-page.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-entry.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-file-entry.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-font-picker.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-mateconf-ui.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-href.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-ice.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-icon-entry.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-icon-item.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-icon-list.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-mdi.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-mdi-child.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-mdi-generic-child.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-pixmap-entry.c: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-popup-menu.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-propertybox.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-scores.c: Likewise.

	* glade/glade-mate.c: Likewise.

	* test-mate/testmate.c: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-appbar.c (mate_appbar_get_progress): Return a
	GtkProgressBar, not a deprecated GtkProgress.
	(mate_appbar_constructor): gtk_widget_set_usize() ->
	gtk_widget_set_size_request().

	* libmateui/mate-color-picker.c
	(mate_color_picker_instance_init): gtk_drawing_area_size() ->
	gtk_widget_set_size_request().
	(cs_ok_clicked): Use the new color selection API.
	(mate_color_picker_clicked): Likewise.
	(mate_color_picker_set_d): gtk_widget_draw() -> gtk_widget_queue_draw().
	(mate_color_picker_set_i8): Likewise.
	(mate_color_picker_set_i16): Likewise.
	(mate_color_picker_set_dither): Likewise.
	(mate_color_picker_set_use_alpha): Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-dateedit.c (position_popup): Use
	gtk_widget_set_uposition() -> gtk_window_move().
	(create_children): gtk_widget_set_usize() ->
	gtk_widget_set_size_request().  gtk_entry_new_with_max_length() ->
	gtk_entry_new() with gtk_entry_set_max_length().
	gtk_window_set_policy() -> gtk_window_set_resizable().

	* libmateui/mate-dialog.c (mate_dialog_init):
	gtk_window_set_policy() -> gtk_window_set_resizable().
	(mate_dialog_set_parent): gtk_widget_set_uposition() ->
	gtk_window_move().

	* libmateui/mate-entry.c (set_combo_items): Re-create the list
	of items for the combo and use gtk_combo_set_popdown_strings().
	We cannot longer use the GtkList deprecated functions.
	(mate_entry_add_history): Keep the items list in the same order
	as specified, and use set_combo_items() instead of inserting the
	item string directly into the GtkCombo list.

	* libmateui/mate-file-entry.c (browse_clicked):
	gtk_widget_set_uposition() -> gtk_window_move().

	* libmateui/mate-font-picker.c: Be stricter in what we don't
	compile when building with GTK_DISABLE_DEPRECATED.
	(mate_font_picker_fi_set_use_font_in_label):
	gtk_widget_restore_default_style() -> gtk_widget_set_style().

	* libmateui/mate-href.c (mate_href_get_text): gtk_label_get()
	-> gtk_label_get_text().

	* libmateui/mate-messagebox.c (mate_message_box_construct):
	gtk_widget_set_usize() -> gtk_widget_set_size_request().

	* libmateui/mate-mdi.c (book_button_release):
	gtk_widget_set_usize() -> gtk_widget_set_size_request().
	(app_create): Removed unneeded gtk_window_set_policy().
	(mate_mdi_set_mode): gtk_widget_set_usize() ->
	gtk_widget_set_size_request().

	* libmateui/mate-mdi-generic-child.c: Be stricter in what we
	don't compile when building with GTK_DISABLE_DEPRECATED.

	* libmateui/mate-mdi-session.c (restore_window_child):
	gtk_widget_set_usize() -> gtk_window_set_default_size().
	gtk_widget_set_uposition() -> gtk_window_move().
	(restore_window): Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-popup-menu.c (relay_popup_button_pressed):
	Don't leak the list of the container's children.

	* libmateui/mate-propertybox.c (dialog_clicked_cb):
	gtk_notebook_current_page() -> gtk_notebook_get_current_page().

	* libmateui/mate-icon-entry.c (browse_clicked):
	gtk_widget_set_usize() -> gtk_widget_set_size_request().
	(ientry_browse): Removed unused gtk_window_set_policy().
	(mate_icon_entry_instance_init): gtk_widget_set_usize() ->
	gtk_widget_set_size_request().

	* libmateui/mate-icon-item.c (iti_start_editing):
	set_uposition() -> window_move().
	(mate_icon_text_item_draw): gtk_draw_focus() ->
	gtk_paint_focus().

	* libmateui/mate-icon-sel.c
	(mate_icon_selection_instance_init): usize() -> size_request().
	(load_idle_func): progress_bar_update() -> progress_bar_set_fraction().

