2002-02-11  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@ximian.com>

	* libmateui/mate-appbar.c (entry_insert_text_cb): Use
	g_signal_stop_emission_by_name().
	(entry_activate_cb): Use g_signal_emit().
	(mate_appbar_refresh): Use gtk_editable_set_editable().
	(mate_appbar_refresh): Use gtk_editable_set_position().
	(mate_appbar_set_progress_percentage): Use
	gtk_progress_bar_set_fraction().

