	g_signal_connect().
	(reply_clear_prompt_cb): Use
	g_signal_handlers_disconnect_by_func().
	(mate_app_set_progress): Use gtk_progress_bar_set_fraction().
	(mate_app_progress_done): Use g_signal_handler_disconnect().

	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c
	(install_menuitem_hint_to_statusbar): Use g_signal_connect() and
	g_object_set_data().
	(create_help_entries): Use g_object_set_data_full().
	(do_ui_signal_connect): Use g_signal_connect_full().

	* libmateui/mate-app.c (mate_app_set_contents): use
	g_signal_connect().

2002-02-11  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@ximian.com>

	* libmateui/mate-app-util.c (ack_clear_prompt_cb): Use
	g_signal_handlers_disconnect_by_func().
	(mate_app_message_bar): Use g_signal_connect().
	(remove_message_timeout): Use g_signal_handler_disconnect().

	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c (showing_pixmaps_changed_notify):
	Use g_object_get_data().
	(remove_notify_cb): Likewise.
	(setup_image_menu_item): Use g_object_set_data().
	(setup_image_menu_item): Use g_object_set_data_full().
	(setup_image_menu_item): Use g_signal_connect().
	(put_hint_in_statusbar): Use g_object_get_data().
	(put_hint_in_appbar): Likewise.
	(create_menu_item): No need to use
	gtk_check_menu_item_set_show_toggle(), which is deprecated and
	silly anyways.
	(help_view_display_callback): Use g_object_get_data().
	(create_help_entries): Use g_signal_connect_closure_by_id().

	* libmateui/mate-app.c (mate_app_instance_init): Use
	g_signal_connect().
	(mate_app_destroy): Use g_object_unref().
	(contents_parent_set): Use g_signal_handlers_disconnect_by_func().
	(mate_app_set_menus): Use g_object_get_data().
	(mate_app_add_toolbar): Likewise.
	(mate_app_add_dock_item): Use g_signal_emit_by_name().

