2002-01-13  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@usa.net>

	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.cc: mate_app_find_menu_pos() was
 	not working, due to a faulty optimisation. I'm not sure what
 	changed since mate-libs 1.2, but the problem is solved by
 	removing the optimisation. This fixes mate_app_insert_menus(),
 	which uses it.

