	  mate-icon-list.c, mate-icon-sel.c, mate-pixmap-entry.c,
	  mate-pixmap.c, mate-scores.c, mate-stock-icons.c,
	  mate-vfs-util.c:  Compile with G_DISABLE_DEPRECATED,
	  GDK_DISABLE_DEPRECATED and GDK_PIXBUF_DISABLE_DEPRECATED, yay!

