	* libmateui/mate-font-picker.c (mate_font_picker_label_use_font_in_label):
	Queue a resize after setting the new style.

	* libmateui/mate-entry.c: Add saving_history to priv struct.
	(mate_entry_history_changed): If we're getting a notification
	from saving our own history, don't reload it.

	* libmateui/mate-app.c (layout_changed): ref/sink the layout.

