	app->layout.

	* libmateui/mate-app-helper.c (do_ui_signal_connect): Use a standard
	signal connection and a thunk to implement the "relay_func"
	feature, rather the (no longer present) marshaller feature
	of gtk_signal_connect_full().

	* libmateui/mate-popup-menu.c (pop_connect_func): Use a thunk rather than
	the (no longer present) marshaller feature of
	gtk_signal_connect_full().

