	* libmateui/mate-font-picker.[ch]: move all fields to the private struct,
	  add an accessor for the 'inside', but only if it's a user set
	  inside.  Change gtkargs to gparams so we get all the new stuff.
	  Add a fixme here and there and minor doc updates

