2001-06-21  Mark Murnane  <Mark.Murnane@Sun.com>

	* libmateui/Changes made during 64-bit cleaning.

	* libmateui/mate-dateedit.c (day_selected): Modified type of day, month and year
	to match signature of gtk_calendar_get_date.

	* libmateui/mate-icon-text.c (mate_icon_layout_text):  Changed w_len and sublen
 	to a gsize.

	* libmateui/mate-less.c (mate_less_write_fd): Changes len and bytes_written to
	a gsize.

	* libmateui/mate-remote_bootstrap.c (main): Changed setenv to putenv.  Solaris
	does not have a setenv libc function.

	* libmateui/mate-unit-spinner.c: Added include directive for string.h.  Required
	to ensure proper forward declaration of strcmp().

2001-06-21  Jens Finke  <jens@mate.org>

	* libmateui/libmateui.h: Don't include mate-animator.h.

