2001-06-16  Christian Rose  <menthos@menthos.com>

	* configure.in: Added sv to ALL_LINGUAS.

2001-06-15  Martin Baulig  <baulig@suse.de>

	* libmateui/mate-mdi.[ch]: Started to port this to MateComponentWindow.

	* libmateui/mate-mdi.h (MateMDIClass): Changed return value of the `add_child',
	`remove_child', `add_view' and `remove_view' virtual functions from
	gint to gboolean. The second argument of the `app_created' virtual
	function is now a `BonboWindow *'.
	(mate_mdi_get_app_from_view): Renamed to mate_mdi_get_window_from_view.
	(mate_mdi_get_active_window): Return a `MateComponentWindow *'.
	(mate_mdi_get_window_from_view): Likewise.
	(mate_mdi_get_view_from_window): Second argument is `MateComponentWindow *'.
	(mate_mdi_set_menubar_template): Second argument is `const gchar *'.
	(mate_mdi_set_toolbar_template): Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-mdi-child.h (MateMDIChildClass): Renamed `set_label' to `get_node'
	and made it return a `MateComponentUINode *'.

2001-06-14  Martin Baulig  <baulig@suse.de>

	* libmateui/mate-textfu.[ch], mate-popup-help.[ch], mate-popup-menu.[ch]: Removed.

	* libmateui/mate-helpsys.[ch], wap-textfu.[ch]: Removed.

