	* libmateui/mate-window.c (mate_window_set_icon_from_default): New function.

2001-06-13  Martin Baulig  <baulig@suse.de>

	* libmateui/Makefile.am: Install libmateui.h in `$(includedir)/mate/2' to make it
	consistent with MateComponent.

	* libmateui/libmateui.h: You now use #include <libmateui.h> to get this.

