	* libmateui/mate-selector-client.[ch]: Moved to libmate-extra/libmateui.
	* libmateui/mate-selector-dialog-client.[ch]: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-selector-component.[ch]: Likewise.

	* libmateui/mate-selector-widget.[ch]: Renamed to mate-component-widget.[ch].

