	* libmateui/mate-selector-client.c
	(mate_selector_client_check_uri): New function.
	(mate_selector_client_scan_directory): New function.

2001-05-31  Martin Baulig  <baulig@suse.de>

	* libmateui/mate-selector-client.c (WANT_PREVIEW_WIDGET): New property.

	* libmateui/mate-selector-component.[ch]: Derive from MateSelector, not
	MateFileSelector which is now a component.
	(MateSelectorComponentClass): Added "ensure_properties" signal.
	(PROP_PREVIEW_WIDGET, PROP_CONTROL_WIDGET): New properties.

2001-05-30  Christophe Merlet  <redfox@eikonex.org>

	* configure.in: Added fr to $ALL_LINGUAS.

2001-05-27  ERDI Gergo  <cactus@cactus.rulez.org>

	* libmateui/mate-about.c: First run at porting it over to
	Pango. It is no longer themed by special widget names in GTKRC,
	instead, you modify the default font for the canvas widget in
	your GTKRC and it will use that. Colors and layout sizes are
	hardcoded for now. Only the title, the copyright and the
	description is displayed (i.e. the authors list is missing).

2001-05-25  Martin Baulig  <baulig@suse.de>

	* libmateui/mate-vfs-util.c (load_done): Use mate_vfs_async_cancel() instead of
	mate_vfs_async_close() on error.

