	all the arguments in the moniker string.

	* libmateui/mate-selector-component.c: Use the new tristate enum.

	* libmateui/mate-image-entry.c, mate-image-selector.c: Only set properties which
	are different from their default values.

	* libmateui/mate-selector-dialog-client.[ch]: New files.

