	* libmateui/mate-entry.[ch]: Move all deprecated functions to libcompat.
	* libmateui/mate-icon-entry.[ch]: Likewise.
	* libmateui/mate-appbar.[ch]: Likewise.

2001-02-23  Martin Baulig  <baulig@suse.de>

	* libmateui/mate-entry.c (mate_entry_set_text, mate_entry_get_text):
	New convenience functions; we need to add them to mate-libs stable
	shortly after MATE 1.4 as well so that people can start to smoothly
	migrate their apps to the new API.

