	* libmateui/mate-selector.h (MateSelector): Added "add_uri" and
	"add_uri_default" signals.
	(mate_selector_add_uri): New function.

	* libmateui/mate-vfs-util.c (file_read_callback): If result == MATE_VFS_OK,
	but bytes_read == 0, we're at the end of the file.

2000-12-06  Martin Baulig  <baulig@suse.de>

	* libmateui/mate-selector.c: Asyncify the "set_filename" signal and the
	mate_selector_set_filename() function.

	* libmateui/mate-entry.c (set_entry_text_handler): `gentry->_priv->entry'
	may be NULL if we don't have the default entry widget.

